an begin="2:25.990" end="2:26.120">の</span><span begin="2:26.180" end="2:27.000">塊</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">无法磨灭的可能性的集合体</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kienai kanousei no katamari</span></p><p begin="2:27.280" end="2:29.720" itunes:key="L40" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:27.280" end="2:27.690">僕</span><span begin="2:27.710" end="2:27.910">ら</span><span begin="2:27.910" end="2:28.120">は</span><span begin="2:28.120" end="2:28.570">今</span><span begin="2:28.570" end="2:28.730">で</span><span begin="2:28.780" end="2:28.970">も</span><span begin="2:28.990" end="2:29.130">負</span><span begin="2:29.210" end="2:29.370">け</span><span begin="2:29.420" end="2:29.640">な</span><span begin="2:29.640" end="2:29.720">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我们至今仍未认输</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Bokura wa ima demo makenai</span></p><p begin="2:30.070" end="2:38.160" itunes:key="L41" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:30.070" end="2:30.880">言</span><span begin="2:30.940" end="2:31.330">葉</span><span begin="2:31.360" end="2:32.010">な</span><span begin="2:32.010" end="2:32.220">ん</span><span begin="2:32.220" end="2:33.060">て</span><span begin="2:33.460" end="2:33.690">い</span><span begin="2:33.710" end="2:34.330">ら</span><span begin="2:34.360" end="2:34.810">な</span><span begin="2:34.810" end="2:35.420">い</span><span begin="2:35.420" end="2:35.660">ん</span><span begin="2:35.660" end="2:38.160">だ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">不需要什么言语</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kotoba nante iranainda</span></p><p begin="2:45.490" end="2:48.420" itunes:key="L42" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:45.490" end="2:46.160">宵</span><span begin="2:46.160" end="2:46.760">闇</span><span begin="2:46.800" end="2:46.990">に</span><span begin="2:46.990" end="2:47.430">溺</span><span begin="2:47.450" end="2:47.660">れ</span><span begin="2:47.680" end="2:47.790">る</span><span begin="2:47.830" end="2:48.240">前</span><span begin="2:48.280" end="2:48.420">に</span><