egin="2:58.370" end="2:58.740">み</span><span begin="2:58.790" end="3:00.400">を</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">将痛楚</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Itami o</span></p><p begin="3:00.890" end="3:03.840" itunes:key="L46" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:00.890" end="3:01.780">痛</span><span begin="3:01.830" end="3:02.160">み</span><span begin="3:02.220" end="3:03.840">を</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">将痛楚</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Itami o</span></p><p begin="3:04.320" end="3:09.040" itunes:key="L47" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:04.320" end="3:05.190">痛</span><span begin="3:05.230" end="3:05.590">み</span><span begin="3:05.630" end="3:08.070">を</span><span begin="3:08.430" end="3:08.540">駆</span><span begin="3:08.650" end="3:08.860">け</span><span begin="3:08.890" end="3:09.040">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">穿越痛楚</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Itami o kakeru</span></p><p begin="3:09.280" end="3:10.800" itunes:key="L48" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:09.280" end="3:09.730">叫</span><span begin="3:09.760" end="3:09.910">ぶ</span><span begin="3:10.150" end="3:10.590">僕</span><span begin="3:10.590" end="3:10.800">ら</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">呐喊的我们</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sakebu bokura</span></p><p begin="3:11.840" end="3:15.040" itunes:key="L49" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:11.840" end="3:11.930">生</span><span begin="3:12.050" end="3:12.280">き</span><span begin="3:12.300" end="3:12.480">る</span><span begin="3:12.690" end="3:12.800">意</span><span begin="3:12.910" end="3:13.110">味</span><span begin="3:13.110" end="3:13.310">を</span><span begin="3:13.550" end="3:13.940">探</span><span begin="3:13.990" end="3:14.150">す</span><span begin="3:14.210" end="3:14.620">僕</span><span begin="3:14.640" end="3:14.850">ら</span><span begin="3:14.880" end="3:15.040">の</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">寻找生存意义的我们</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Ikiru imi o sagasu bokura no</span