.540" end="3:24.640">い</span><span begin="3:24.710" end="3:24.900">ま</span><span begin="3:24.920" end="3:25.130">ま</span><span begin="3:25.150" end="3:25.310">だ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我们至今仍未知晓</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Bokura wa ima demo shiranai mama da</span></p><p begin="3:25.560" end="3:26.180" itunes:key="L53" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:25.560" end="3:25.660">だ</span><span begin="3:25.760" end="3:26.000">け</span><span begin="3:26.020" end="3:26.180">ど</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">但是</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Dakedo</span></p><p begin="3:26.440" end="3:28.730" itunes:key="L54" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:26.440" end="3:26.860">僕</span><span begin="3:26.860" end="3:27.040">ら</span><span begin="3:27.280" end="3:27.480">に</span><span begin="3:27.500" end="3:27.730">は</span><span begin="3:27.730" end="3:28.130">歌</span><span begin="3:28.170" end="3:28.380">が</span><span begin="3:28.380" end="3:28.590">あ</span><span begin="3:28.590" end="3:28.730">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我们拥有歌</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Bokura ni wa uta ga aru</span></p><p begin="3:29.010" end="3:32.180" itunes:key="L55" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:29.010" end="3:29.420">僕</span><span begin="3:29.420" end="3:29.620">ら</span><span begin="3:29.870" end="3:30.050">に</span><span begin="3:30.080" end="3:30.290">は</span><span begin="3:30.290" end="3:30.660">愛</span><span begin="3:30.720" end="3:30.920">が</span><span begin="3:30.940" end="3:31.500">残</span><span begin="3:31.500" end="3:31.580">っ</span><span begin="3:31.580" end="3:31.770">て</span><span begin="3:31.770" end="3:31.970">い</span><span begin="3:32.010" end="3:32.180">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我们还有爱残留</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Bokura ni wa ai ga nokotteiru</span></p><p begin="3:32.430" end="3:35.570" itunes:key="L56" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:32.430" end="3:32.880">答</span><span begin="3:32.880" end="